MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 988

CREATING AND DESIGNATING PARCELS OF LAND OF THE PRIVATE DOMAIN SITUATED AT BARANGAY BULAC, STA. MARIA, BULACAN, AS A SPECIAL ECONOMIC ZONE PURSUANT TO REPUBLIC ACT NO. 7916 AS AMENDED BY REPUBLIC ACT NO. 8748

Pursuant to the powers vested in me under Republic Act No. 7916, otherwise known as the Special Economic Zone Act of 1995 as amended and upon recommendation of the Board of Directors of the Philippine Economic Zone Authority, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL – ARROYO , President of the Philippines, do hereby create and designate, subject to the provisions of Republic Act No. 7916, as amended, its Implementing Rules and Regulations and Resolution No. 99-001 dated 13 January 1999 of the Board of Directors of the Philippine Economic Zone Authority, an area located at Barangay Bulac, Sta. Maria, Bulacan, as a special economic zone, consisting of THREE HUNDRED THIRTY TWO THOUSAND THREE HUNDRED SIXTEEN (332,316.00) Square Meters as defined by the following technical description:

